    "content" : "If not been changed in the past then earlies up to '62...crossover year 63 had bit of both..ie late spindle early links. And 63 on have late spindles. Still best to do as said and pull the drum and check. I ordered up a kit for my old 62 single cab some years back and ordered for earlies and it had been changed to late at some point before I got it. Lesson learnt \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> always bother to check first \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\">",
    "lastEdited" : "Tue Mar 22, 2016 8:46 pm"
  }, {
